Package com.example.bot.spring.textsender

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Broadcaster
    interface that all broadcast should implement
    TextSender
    interface of all text senders
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BookingTextSender
    handle the book request implement a pipeline model to handle the user input and match it with a good trip
    CancelBroadcaster
    if the trip is canceled due to not enough people, inform all the users that subscribe to the trips
    ConfirmBroadcaster
    once the trip is confirmed to go, notify all the users that subscribe to the trip
    DoubleElevBroadcaster
    added features that the clients could give some special discount on special date this function is to inform all the users that there will be a discount
    GQTextSender
    general questions handler which could ask questions like how long is the trip and when the trip will begin
    RecommendationTextSender
    handle the recommendation from the user and recommend some trips according to the features
    SQTextSender
    implement the simple questions like greetings
    UQAnswerReplier
    if someone answers the questions on the website, it will send the message to the user and update the table
    UQAutomateSender
    handle the unanswered questions
